Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:57.04,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}サカラバ　サア
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:02:02.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}静けき森の中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:08.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}いま目覚めた花たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:14.06,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}この世に何を思い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:21.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}何を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:25.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}ああ　真実ほど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:33.29,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}人を魅了するものはないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:37.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}ああ　真実ほど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:44.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}人に残酷なものもないのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:47.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}咲き誇れ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}想いのままに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:53.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}この瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:57.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}全てを賭けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:02.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}無限の星すらも霞むように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:08.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}勇気　心に溢れ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:18.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}いかなる時も生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:57.04,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}盛开吧 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:02:02.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}静谧的森林之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:08.94,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}刚醒来的花儿们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:14.06,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}如何看待这世间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:21.11,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}有什么样的感触
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:25.48,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}没有什么比真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:33.29,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}更加让人心醉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:37.60,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}没有什么比真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:44.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}更加对人残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:47.55,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}尽情绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.65,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}随心飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:53.56,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}在此瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:57.09,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}拼上一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:02.65,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}遮蔽无限星空的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:08.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}勇气充满心间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:18.03,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\fad(300,300)}永远生活下去
