Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是吧 难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太好了 姐姐你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那个…大家的样子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}于是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}树 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}被选中了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这种现象被称为树海化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}时间停滞下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}被选为勇者的我们被送往神树大人所创造的结界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大赦派遣来的风学姐将勇者适应值较高的少女收集起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}创立了勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是人类的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者为了让世界免受Vertex这一神秘生命体的袭击而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一旦Vertex抵达神树大人 世界就会毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了阻止它 我们展现出战斗的意志 成为神树大人的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}世界说不定会毁灭 大家也面临着危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而我却没能展现出意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然而 友奈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不要那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}看着别人受到伤害 经历苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}与其让别人经历这样的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不如由我来努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者冲拳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者部的活动内容是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了大家鼓起勇气做好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是赞州中学勇者部 结城友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我来成为勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没跟你们说真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那怎么不早点把勇者部真正的意义告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈和树说不定会死的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是就算勇者适应性再高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}哪个小队会被神树大人选中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在敌人来之前是无法知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为这是涉及人类存亡的头等大事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一直瞒着我们…这么重要的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要是只有我一个人无法变身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就会成为勇者部的累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对输给恐惧的自己感到羞愧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对风学姐说了过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为正是由于适应性让我与风学姐和树相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是因为这适应性？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}以后也会很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只是多了有点困难的任务而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也很高兴与大家相识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}保护这个世界是我们的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}倘若我也有保护我珍爱的朋友的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:07:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要欺负友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}据风学姐所说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要打倒十二只Vertex 我们的任务也就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而且大赦还派遣了经过特别训练的夏凛加入我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一开始对勇者部持否定态度的夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也渐渐地敞开心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大家度过着珍爱的日常 憧憬着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要保护好这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}剩下七只
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么全部都攻过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真是最糟糕的袭击模式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}出阵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好 去歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们也上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}将积蓄的能量释放出来 就是勇者的王牌「盛开」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}通过不断地盛开 勇者的力量将得到增幅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大赦是这样说明的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}面对着剩下的七只Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们相继地盛开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「盛开」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大家干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了庆祝勇者部大胜利 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}目标达成之后的果汁果然就是不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在那场战斗中经历了盛开的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}身体都出现了异常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈是味觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}风学姐是左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}树是声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是左耳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然大赦的医生说应该马上就会痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但却完全没有好转的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然后 我知道了勇者系统的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我一直在呼唤你呀 鹫鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真是想死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她的名字叫做乃木园子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她用那悲伤的眼神紧盯着我 称呼我为鹫鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈经历过「盛开」对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一下开放 一下变强的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对 经历过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也经历过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们觉得绽放盛开的花之后会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}盛开之后 身体应该有什么部位会变得不方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我觉得大赦的人们掩盖这一系统也算是一种同情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不过 我真的好想被好好告知这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要是早知道会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就会更珍惜和朋友玩耍的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那个发带真适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这条发带是非常重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我只记得这些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没办法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么了 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}突然叫我们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我有东西想给风学姐和友奈看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东…东乡同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者绝不会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了确认前代勇者乃木园子所言是否属实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我使用了各种手段寻死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\fs45\1c&H3F473C&\frx318\fry354\frz28.62\move(717,375,687,-36,0,3253)}切腹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\fs45\1c&H3F473C&\frx318\fry354\frz28.62\move(792,483,762,90,41,3253)}上吊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\fs45\1c&H3F473C&\frx318\fry354\frz26.03\move(969,564,939,165,41,3253)}跳楼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\fs45\1c&H3F473C&\frz21.5\frx320\fry354\move(1182,630,1164,231,41,3253)}一氧化碳中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\fs45\1c&H3F473C&\frx320\fry354\frz29.6\move(1005,828,975,432,41,3253)}淹死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.37,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\fs45\1c&H3F473C&\frx320\fry354\frz29.6\move(1059,951,1029,549,41,3253)}服毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}无论尝试何种方法 精灵都成功地阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}精灵并不是为了保护勇者 而是为了将勇者永远束缚在其使命上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也就是说 乃木园子所言属实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们的后遗症是盛开这一力量的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是供品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那么 树就再也无法发出声音了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了保护别人而献上自己的身躯进行战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这就是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:13:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}都怪我把树拉进勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:06.23,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}出会えてよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:13.25,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}木漏れ日 眩しい森の中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:18.37,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}風はいつもあったかくて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:25.02,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}心ほぐれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:31.12,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}こんな日々がずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:37.81,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}続きますように
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:46.10,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}広がる空は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:50.99,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}愛や希望で溢れて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:57.50,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}この声が届くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:03.89,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}歌い続けるから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:14.17,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}いつも　いつもありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:28.10,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}この声が届くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:33.90,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}歌い続けるから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:44.60,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}いつも　いつもありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:06.23,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}庆幸与你邂逅于
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:13.25,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}光斑炫目的林间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:18.37,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}风总是那么温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:25.02,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}心灵也随之解放
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:31.12,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}但愿这样的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:37.81,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}永远地持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:46.10,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}如此广阔的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:50.99,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}充满着爱与希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:57.50,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我会不停地歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:03.89,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}直至传入你心间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:14.17,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}一直一直感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:28.10,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我会不停地歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:33.90,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}直至传入你心间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:44.60,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}一直一直感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}听我说…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我有目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是说有未来的梦想了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那快告诉姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}保密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不会跟别人说的 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有一天会告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我要干掉大赦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大赦欺骗了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}盛开的后遗症是治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么非得受这份罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么非得让树失声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么非得放弃梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}拯救了世界的代价就是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}让开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不想看到风学姐伤害别人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这种事情怎能饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是即便是告知我们会有后遗症
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们还是会战斗下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了保卫世界只能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没有人有别的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对不起 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:46.65,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\fs45\rnd8\1c&H294776&\frz1.253\frx356\fry358\move(756,378,360,111,0,4289)}要是没有与勇者部的大家相遇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:46.65,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\fs45\rnd8\1c&H294776&\frz1.253\frx356\fry358\move(693,555,324,294,35,4289)}一定也不会拥有想歌唱的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:46.65,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnHiragino Sans GB W3\bord0\b0\fs45\rnd8\1c&H294776&\frz1.253\frx356\fry358\move(837,840,468,597,35,4289)}能加入勇者部真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你冷静地听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我来告诉你墙壁外侧的秘密 这个世界的构成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}听好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我觉得真相还是由你自己的眼睛来见证比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她所说的都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}世界在宇宙规模的结界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Vertex无限再生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们一边奉献着身体的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一边重复着永无止尽的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而最终…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}身体就像树木一样无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}最终就像这样被侍奉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我得出的结论是破坏墙壁打倒神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要从勇者这一祭品中摆脱出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就只有破坏神树大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我无法忍受大家再受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}树…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么…还要坚持…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不知道为什么 突然想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不论是家里的事还是勇者部的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}把麻烦事都交给姐姐来做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是 其实我想让自己能与姐姐并肩前行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}何止是并肩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不知不觉间已经走到我前面了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么无法变身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不配当…朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不再作为大赦的勇者而战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}从现在开始作为勇者部的一员而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不会让我们的勇者部遭到毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不想看到友奈哭泣的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真是傻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}诸行无常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}来吧 好戏从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:18:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}远处的家伙们听好了 近处的家伙们看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这就是赞州中学二年级生 勇者部部员三好夏凛的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}来 吃招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在这即将来临的新世界中 风学姐和树就不需要再战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者部五准则 其五
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有志者事竟成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛也不要再失去什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:19:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这个世界 大赦的做法 有多么凄惨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要拯救我们 就只有这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「谢谢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我长期以来一直接受勇者的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只有战斗才是我的存在价值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是多亏了大家 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈你能够改变东乡的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一定能够
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}盛开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我曾经作为勇者战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然后失去了这段记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}既然我保护不了我最好的朋友 那我就做不成勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要能将一切终结 我们的人间地狱也会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}与其牺牲友奈和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}与其再次忘记这珍爱的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}东乡同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我永远陪伴着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样的话就不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太阳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我做了这么过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这不是东乡同学的错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们去阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}阻止不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}绝对不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我的脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对不起 在这关键的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}风学姐 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}欢迎回来 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:53.42,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.02,0:21:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不要小看勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好 勇者部…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5\alpha&HA0&}友奈姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}击中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者部的大家 明明也都很艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但却为了朋友 拼尽全力 阻止了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}友奈全力冲向了我 全力抱紧了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以 我不再害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然后我们击败了敌人 身体功能也恢复了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.47,0:23:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我重要的回忆 也恢复了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然还不清楚为什么会恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但至少这不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为失去的生命 并没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一起去上学 学习 玩耍 回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.93,0:23:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}日常竟然是如此珍贵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.62,0:23:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我很清楚 一切并没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Vertex还残存着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.43,0:23:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不知道未来还会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.58,0:23:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是现在 我紧紧地拥抱着这无可替代的温暖
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.88,0:22:45.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}さあ　歩き出そう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.19,0:22:48.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}みんなで見た　あの空模様
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.29,0:22:51.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}光のカーテン　しめきっても
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.90,0:22:53.79,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ここは暗くない
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.79,0:22:55.79,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}もう　分かってたの
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.79,0:22:58.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}いつか終わる　この瞬間
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.88,0:23:02.69,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}とても大切で　大切で
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}目を背けていた
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.10,0:23:07.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}儚い時は
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.19,0:23:10.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あっという間に過ぎて行くよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.08,0:23:12.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}これは本当に
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.12,0:23:15.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}起こった出来事？
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.29,0:23:17.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そのカケラを夕陽に
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.87,0:23:20.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}かざして確かめてみるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.66,0:23:22.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れられない
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.87,0:23:25.63,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れちゃいけない
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.63,0:23:32.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ひとつひとつが素晴らしい思い出
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.66,0:23:37.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}いつでも　目に浮かぶその笑顔
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.19,0:23:43.59,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ひとつひとつが奇跡なんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:43.59,0:23:49.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ここにこうして舞い降りてきたの
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.93,0:23:55.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So bright
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.88,0:22:45.19,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}来　迈开脚步吧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.19,0:22:48.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}大家看到的天空
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.29,0:22:51.90,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}即便拉上光之帘
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.90,0:22:53.79,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这里也并不黑暗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.79,0:22:55.79,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我现在已经明白
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.79,0:22:58.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这瞬间终将结束
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.88,0:23:02.69,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这是那么的宝贵
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.69,0:23:04.89,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我不禁避开视线
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.10,0:23:07.19,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}梦幻般的时刻
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.19,0:23:10.08,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}真是转瞬即逝
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.08,0:23:12.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这是真真正正
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.12,0:23:15.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}发生过的事吗
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.29,0:23:17.87,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}残片对着夕阳
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.87,0:23:20.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}来试着确认吧
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.66,0:23:22.87,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这些无法忘却
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.87,0:23:25.63,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}这些不能忘却
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.63,0:23:32.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}每每都是美妙回忆
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.66,0:23:37.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}总是回想起那笑容
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.19,0:23:43.59,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}每每都是一份奇迹
Dialogue: 1,0:23:43.59,0:23:49.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}就像这样降临于此
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.93,0:23:55.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So bright
